freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: My right arm (arm I got the last shot) has been turning blue/purple. I've also had intermittent red rashes on my shoulder. My lymph nodes are swollen. Dizzy. Earache. Fatigue. Pre syncope. Legs intermittently get really cold and blue. Extremely weak
Shortness of breath, sinus pressure, low oxygen, intermittent fever, fatigue, horrible headache for days, swollen lymph nodes, new lung mass I have had lung CT before and after vaccine.
